        "displayName": "Doug Cutting",
        "active": true,
        "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
      },
      "body": "I'm closing this.  The default configuration supports standalone, in-process operation, and there's a well-documented way to achieve standalone multi-process operation (aka \"pseudo distributed').",
